msg":"自己跟團去會唔會好悶"},{"pid":"87df2d2722e48a21d3783e21f89eeeaa15996662","tid":1013272,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02cb70435e06a6e595768b93e5669434d03bf82b","tid":1013272,"uid":69913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"自己跟團去會唔會好悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"睇住人地一對對，一家人，一班朋友，而自己孤伶伶個感覺一定好撚爽。當然大家都會希望同你溝通下，例如問你借尿袋呀，幫手影下相呀咁。"},{"pid":"acdc6c8deebfefd9456e86d7c4160373031ee661","tid":1013272,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"上年跟美麗華<br />\n幾好<br />\n$15000有找包零用手信<br />\n河TRIP唔洗用腦夠HEA"},{"pid":"bee5cf63ad27eddd0895ad84ce65a28bdb7024a1","tid":1013272,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"諗緊下個月去 <br />\n係以色列入好似好麻煩咁<br />\n有冇人有經驗陸路入？"},{"pid":"2850f4c20ec8407c477d9f131841ce1f04a7c70b","tid":1013272,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"埃及<br />\n跟團比較好<br />\n<br />\n始終唔係日本，台灣"},{"pid":"dcd4053729a13c146c5da45d0adbc9ebac9d6482","tid":1013272,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"去埃及梗係跟金怡假期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad38d8582632bd281b6c4ea7ff14f087b48273c","tid":1013272,"uid":14657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"想月尾跟美麗華去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一條友好悶咁"},{"pid":"1e1cc18a05519c2a5b84b4a1fa9f18b22c7013b8","tid":1013272,"uid":222136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad38d8582632bd281b6c4ea7ff14f087b48273c","tid":1013272,"uid":14657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"想月尾跟美麗華去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一條友好悶咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"心動不如行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ea9d133274cfd05a07023979fc409c45d5249e","tid":1013272,"uid":29469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd4053729a13c146c5da45d0adbc9ebac9d6482","tid":1013272,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"去埃及梗係跟金怡假期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"我之前都係跟金怡去，成個trip 最幾正<br />\n最舒服係4日係船上面<br />\n個導遊好似歷史老師咁，超詳細講解埃及歷史"},{"pid":"c41396dab57c7b49244239eb2a59f148fc0a7cb4","tid":1013272,"uid":125489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"11年跟永安團去過<br />\n<br />\n團費6999<br />\n<br />\n當時係暴動冇幾耐之後，博物館隔離棟建築物仲燒到黒晒<br />\n<br />\n除咗阿歷山大港同洪加達之外應該基本要去嘅地方都去咗<br />\n<br />\n行程有一晚瞓火車，唔記得3晚定4晚瞓遊船，仲有一晚瞓沙漠<br />\n<br />\n整體我覺得唔錯，個領隊又跟得幾好（睇落廿尾後生仔）<br />\n<br />\n全程接觸到嘅阿拉伯人冇見過偷嘢搶嘢，頂籠都係呃吓錢找少錢咁"},{"pid":"e798109e160572d04c6a156ec38dc1f5df107316","tid":1013272,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"前年單拖去過兩星期<br />\n埃及D人講煩都無埃塞俄比亞咁煩<br />\n識英文又主動同你講野100%唔係好人<br />\n如果有D Art sense或者想睇真係靚既廟<br />\n咁你要係Luxor自己包架車去Abydos同埋Dendara呢兩個廟<br />\n以藝術同埋觀賞度應該係成個埃及最top<br />\n<br />\n帆船自己講吓價<br />\n我Aswan同Luxor都坐過<br />\n無乜分別<br />\n埃及人有時會暇你無pretty cash找零<br />\n其實係一定有<br />\n仲有庶汁、烤雞同埋koshary都一定要試下"},{"pid":"64e3cf7c997b41a24f830c404b3da6047a5e7146","tid":1013272,"uid":192358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T23:05:36.000Z","msg":"想去好多年，一直都喺跟團同自遊行中猶豫，<br />\n跟團得8日，一定趕，但好在唔洗煩同有導遊解釋景點，<br />\n但我想玩半個月，用半日欣賞金字塔（聽講跟團得30分鐘）"},{"pid":"25c47c8a2b8c6f4c194f33fea9bc4929d07a4d36","tid":1013272,"uid":37203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:35:22.000Z","msg":"去咗9日，基本日日睇神殿，除咗係沙漠玩下衝沙同去紅海游下水同坐熱氣球，其他幾日都好鬼悶"},{"pid":"e088751ad895cc5af97d6e19d2020e896d74720c","tid":1013272,"uid":74415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bee5cf63ad27eddd0895ad84ce65a28bdb7024a1","tid":1013272,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"諗緊下個月去 <br />\n係以色列入好似好麻煩咁<br />\n有冇人有經驗陸路入？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"係Eilat搭巴士落boarder好快，但過關好撚煩，離境稅要比兩次，因為香港護照免簽證，出左境既地方叫Taba，每日得兩班車落Dahab，最好睇定時間。<br />\n如果唔係要上啲埃及佬呃錢車，好撚7貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以stay兩三日係Dahab，隔離紅海潛下水浮潛下 個景一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後再搭8個鐘巴士入開羅，其間係西奈範圍既check point要係咁落車檢查行李。"},{"pid":"54a62ba080f0e38cbe3ee70815b5f2b7f1d143ea","tid":1013272,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"講咁耐都冇人比張相黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaedb160525554d5cc5420da9616ff0e494f4d7","tid":1013272,"uid":70452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"想一條友去，但好似唔跟團去買好多入場劵都會俾人水"},{"pid":"232123adbc1d20a9b466207b94706d7d23af3203","tid":1013272,"uid":209996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e088751ad895cc5af97d6e19d2020e896d74720c","tid":1013272,"uid":74415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bee5cf63ad27eddd0895ad84ce65a28bdb7024a1","tid":1013272,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"諗緊下個月去 <br />\n係以色列入好似好麻煩咁<br />\n有冇人有經驗陸路入？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"係Eilat搭巴士落boarder好快，但過關好撚煩，離境稅要比兩次，因為香港護照免簽證，出左境既地方叫Taba，每日得兩班車落Dahab，最好睇定時間。<br />\n如果唔係要上啲埃及佬呃錢車，好撚7貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以stay兩三日係Dahab，隔離紅海潛下水浮潛下 個景一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後再搭8個鐘巴士入開羅，其間係西奈範圍既check point要係咁落車檢查行李。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"所言甚是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關口5分鐘就入左埃及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我遇到個關員就唔識香港 唔知道係Visa free <br />\n你要印定/cap定官網呀 特區護照係免簽證！<br />\n跟住 Taba 去 Cairo 一日得一班車（3點鐘）<br />\n公司叫 East Delta Bus<br />\n去 dahab 或者係有多一班 唔清楚 <br />\n上車要比車費（去dahab好似係60LE) +出關費 400LE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我係 Dahab 落車住左晚，潛水好撚正<br />\n唔識游水都可以潛，食野好平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沿路會停好多次 check passport"},{"pid":"df6122b699ea25ac2ab432eb00d8eb0ce9e8d6d7","tid":1013272,"uid":209996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e798109e160572d04c6a156ec38dc1f5df107316","tid":1013272,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"前年單拖去過兩星期<br />\n埃及D人講煩都無埃塞俄比亞咁煩<br />\n識英文又主動同你講野100%唔係好人<br />\n如果有D Art sense或者想睇真係靚既廟<br />\n咁你要係Luxor自己包架車去Abydos同埋Dendara呢兩個廟<br />\n以藝術同埋觀賞度應該係成個埃及最top<br />\n<br />\n帆船自己講吓價<br />\n我Aswan同Luxor都坐過<br />\n無乜分別<br />\n埃及人有時會暇你無pretty cash找零<br />\n其實係一定有<br />\n仲有庶汁、烤雞同埋koshary都一定要試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T20:04:10.000Z","msg":"埃塞人好nice wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 埃及煩好多<br />\n追住唔停，你屌佢佢仲還口添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟團無咁多scam囉<br />\n一街都係，搭車、買野、入境點、騎駱駝、影相<br />\n全部野都會遇到scam <br />\n主動講英文既十成十係呃人<br />\n千萬不要信埃及人！<br />\n<br />\n岩岩去完開羅同Luxor <br />\n開羅有uber可以自遊行 <br />\nluxor超誇張，勁多scam, 加上景點好難自己去哂，都要跟local tour <br />\n好平，東岸西岸各自係 50-70LE (tips excluded) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GKYjau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GKYjau.png&h=c632fe34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂蜀神廟 <br />\n門口失落左既方尖碑就係賣左去法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係協和廣場"},{"pid":"65140d4f9476fd232a9a89f13624e8f67f2439a4","tid":1013272,"uid":98715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"暑假去係咪好熱？佢地嘅熱係咪辛苦過香港好多？"},{"pid":"aaeffb2b15871e7ea354ce6d20c7f53f8f3b9537","tid":1013272,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"想坐埃及航空，跟團做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94242c4af3f9505e99cb6d1a7472133d1f5a4754","tid":1013272,"uid":233557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"報左團5月尾去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f9b9816f56f4c7bd7476f272d5c3af28712d36","tid":1013272,"uid":222136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94242c4af3f9505e99cb6d1a7472133d1f5a4754","tid":1013272,"uid":233557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"報左團5月尾去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"師兄跟邊間"},{"pid":"6ed02fa80c51b87ea1ed352f3539b0a077b61d01","tid":1013272,"uid":191864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61779382007d283696b24a853c7b20c6c312ac4c","tid":1013272,"uid":36533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"咩叫one dollar one dollar"},{"pid":"86c249e7045fe82cad6de1f9a1e708016b653741","tid":1013272,"uid":233557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f9b9816f56f4c7bd7476f272d5c3af28712d36","tid":1013272,"uid":222136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94242c4af3f9505e99cb6d1